Package Models

Class Data

  • java.lang.Object
    • Models.Data
  • public class Data
extends java.lang.Object
    This class essentially holds all of the database information locally. It was becoming more and more difficult to write disparate code to deal with the data on each form. This acts like the Inventory object in the Software 1 class.
